chapters.title: Turk, Carla, and the Best Relationship

description:
I hadn't watched Scrubs much when it first aired. There was something about it that never really spoke to me. Having watched it in full though, I definitely feel as though I missed something. This video is a look at the highs and lows of the series. The stuff it got right, and the stuff it got wrong. I hope people enjoy it.

If you like sitcom retrospectives, check out my channel for plenty of others covering shows from the 1980s to the 2000s.

11:38 - The Price of Healthcare

59:54 - Janitor
1:03:35 - Daydreams, Death, and Doctoring
